OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1782616677
OL,3,CYvette Cooper: Burnham should increase
OL,4,Cdefence spending 'further and faster'
OL,6,FForeign Secretary Yvette Cooper has
OL,7,Ftold me that the government is
OL,8,Fincreasing defence spending too
OL,9,Fslowly. She said it is imperative to
OL,10,Fmove "further and faster" than the
OL,11,Fcurrent plans, to ensure the 3% of GDP
OL,12,Ftarget is met.
OL,14,FAhead of the publication of the
OL,15,FDefence Investment Plan, or "DIP" next
OL,16,Fweek - which is set to be Sir Keir
OL,17,FStarmer's last big initiative as PM -
OL,18,Fshe said in an exclusive ITV News
OL,19,Finterview that the funding element of
OL,20,Fthe DIP was inadequate.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
