FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1782616677
OL,3,CYvette Cooper: Burnham should increase
OL,4,Cdefence spending 'further and faster'
OL,6,FShe is siding with John Healey, who
OL,7,Fresigned as defence secretary last
OL,8,Fmonth because of his deep concern that
OL,9,FStarmer's plan to spend just 2.68% of
OL,10,FGDP on defence is imperilling the
OL,11,Fcountry's security.
OL,13,FCooper is also highlighting a major
OL,14,Fdilemma for Andy Burnham for the early
OL,15,Fweeks of his time in office, if he
OL,16,Fbecomes prime minister, because he
OL,17,Fwon't be able to find the extra #15
OL,18,Fbillion a year, or so Cooper believes
OL,19,Fis needed for defence.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
