OL,3,CYvette Cooper: Burnham should increase
OL,4,Cdefence spending 'further and faster'
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FHer intervention will increase
OL,12,Fpressure on him to spell out how he
OL,13,Fwill reconcile his many priorities
OL,14,Fthat are all competing for additional
OL,15,Fmoney, including major reforms to
OL,16,Freduce the cost of energy and housing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
