OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1782616677
OL,3,CYvette Cooper: Burnham should increase
OL,4,Cdefence spending 'further and faster'
OL,6,FBurnham is yet to say whether he will
OL,7,Fincrease taxation - or can accelerate
OL,8,Fsavings from welfare reform - given
OL,9,Fthat his commitment to stay within the
OL,10,Ffiscal rules would make it impossible
OL,11,Fto borrow significantly more.
OL,13,FI was speaking to Cooper as she
OL,14,Fvisited a military encampment near the
OL,15,FRussian border, where British, Polish,
OL,16,FAmerican and other NATO troops are
OL,17,Fengaged in continuous exercises and
OL,18,Fpreparations for a possible Russian
OL,19,Finvasion.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
