PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1782616677
OL,3,CYvette Cooper: Burnham should increase
OL,4,Cdefence spending 'further and faster'
OL,6,FI pointed out that Poland will this
OL,7,Fyear spend 4.8% of its national income
OL,8,Fon defence, not quite double what the
OL,9,FUK spends.
OL,11,FShe did not dismiss concerns raised by
OL,12,Fthe recently retired Deputy Supreme
OL,13,FCommander of NATO, Keith Blount in an
OL,14,Finterview with The Times, that the UK
OL,15,Fcould lose its entitlement to always
OL,16,Fhave a British national in that
OL,17,Fimportant NATO post, unless it
OL,18,Faccelerates the rise in defence
OL,19,Fspending to 3% of GDP.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
